Linux Troubleshooting Scenario

Overview

Support send an alert, one our service are intermittingly down. Support advises that one of our servers
has high latency issues, a high CPU load average, and cannot run a diagnostic application on the
server. Which command(s) and files should the SRE review to resolve the issue?

Time Permitting:

Please be prepared to discuss how you might:
• Gather more information from the Support Engineer
• Decide when to escalate
• How would you conduct an RCA
• Runbook Documentation

Final Deliverable
Please create a pull/merge request that shows a ReadMe and a Runbook of how you might resolve the Linux Server Issue.
